lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps wasn't competing on opening night of the U.S. Olympic swimming trials. Still, the 18-time gold medalist's influence impacted the results in the 400-meter individual medley, an event he once dominated.

headline.main: Phelps' Influence Out of Pool Impacts Results at US Trials
